It's so nice to see you again.

14:24.363 --> 14:26.866
- Oh, thank you, Ms. Donna.

14:26.932 --> 14:28.834
Thank you for having me.
You look amazing.

14:28.901 --> 14:30.236
- Oh, thank you.

14:30.336 --> 14:32.438
