22:50.369 --> 22:52.337
- Come here. Sit down.

22:52.404 --> 22:56.842
<i>[hopeful music playing]</i>

22:56.908 --> 23:00.746
<i>- And to my son, Marcus.</i>
<i>Where are you, Marcus?</i>

23:00.846 --> 23:04.449
<i>Jovan, my son is MIA.</i>
<i>You getting this?</i>

23:04.549 --> 23:06.017
<i>- [laughing]</i>

23:06.084 --> 23:08.286
<i>- To Marcus,</i>
<i>who has the biggest heart</i>

23:08.387 --> 23:10.021
<i>of anyone I know.</i>

23:10.088 --> 23:12.891
<i>We all go through a tough</i>
