23:26.571 --> 23:33.478
<i>♪ ♪</i>

23:33.578 --> 23:35.580
- Thanks, Mom.

23:47.559 --> 23:49.561
- I'm sorry about the Benz.

23:54.099 --> 23:55.600
- You may enter.

23:57.736 --> 23:59.971
Mm.

24:00.071 --> 24:02.174
